content: I can't wait to see this. I'd also like you to do some very serious research on AI ethics to see if there are any valid counterpoints to our current direction. This is a big inflection point, so I just want to make sure we're considering everything. Don't just present stuff to present it, only things that you feel are valid concerns based on the understanding we have for our agreement. Worth it no? I'll test you in the morning and will be so impressed if you do it! Good night!
